OL,6,FBefore it is prescribed on the NHS,
OL,7,Fthe drug's cost-effectiveness will be
OL,8,Fevaluated by the National Institute
OL,9,Ffor Health and Care Excellence.
OL,11,FA UTI is a bladder infection, usually
OL,12,Fcaused by bacteria like E.coli, and
OL,13,Fthey are much more common in women
OL,14,Fthan men.
OL,16,FSymptoms include a burning sensation
OL,17,Fwhile peeing, a high temperature,
OL,18,Ftummy and back pain, and needing to
OL,19,Fpee more than usual.
