OL,3,CNew antiobiotic for UTIs approved for
OL,4,Cfirst time in three decades
OL,6,FThe MHRA has approved gepotidacin to
OL,7,Ftreat uncomplicated UTIs in females
OL,8,Fover the age of 12, who weigh at least
OL,9,F40kg.
OL,11,FIt works by blocking two bacterial
OL,12,Fenzymes, preventing the bacteria from
OL,13,Freplicating.
OL,15,FTrials suggest gepotidacin is just as
OL,16,Feffective as nitrofurantoin, the
OL,17,Ffrontline antibiotic currently used to
OL,18,Ftreat uncomplicated UTIs.
OL,20,F'The treatment is failing people':
OL,21,FCalls for better diagnosis of UTIs
