OL,3,CNew antiobiotic for UTIs approved for
OL,4,Cfirst time in three decades
OL,6,FJulian Beach, interim executive
OL,7,Fdirector of healthcare quality and
OL,8,Faccess at the MHRA, said: "Keeping
OL,9,Fpatients safe and enabling their
OL,10,Faccess to high quality, safe and
OL,11,Feffective medicines are key priorities
OL,12,Ffor us.
OL,14,F"As the first new type of oral
OL,15,Fantibiotic to treat uncomplicated UTIs
OL,16,Fto be approved in nearly three
OL,17,Fdecades, gepotidacin provides a new
OL,18,Ftreatment option for women facing
OL,19,Frecurrent infections that can severely
OL,20,Fimpact daily life.
