OL,6,F"The antibiotic's targeted mechanism
OL,7,Fof action makes it more difficult for
OL,8,Fbacteria to develop treatment
OL,9,Fresistance ` a crucial factor as drug-
OL,10,Fresistant bacteria are increasingly on
OL,11,Fthe rise globally."
OL,13,FIt is recommended that patients take
OL,14,Ftwo gepotidacin twice a day for five
OL,15,Fdays, around every 12 hours.
